ls and the big. Most of the designs come from a time when clocks were slower and craftsmanship was still a tradition.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">The production takes place by hand assembly and individual control in the pencil city of Nuremberg.</span></p></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><script>window.__gemStoreData = {};window.__gemStoreData.gemKeyValid = {};window.__gemStoreData.gemKeyValid.bestWayAddToCart = 1;</script></div><div id="divContentBk"></div><!--End_Gem_Page_Main_Editor-->
